					<description><![CDATA[<p>Advanced prostate cancer is cancer that has spread beyond the prostate to distant parts of the body. It is also called metastatic or&amp;#160;stage 4 prostate cancer. While most advanced prostate cancer is incurable, treatments can slow or shrink the cancer, reduce symptoms and extend a person's life. Recent advancements in diagnostic techniques and new treatments [&amp;#8230;]</p>
